            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EWisdom%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20riches%20are%20the%20three%20goals%20that%20the%20world%20passionately%20pursues.%20Anyone%20who%20achieves%20status%20in%20one%20of%20these%20three%20areas%20is%20celebrated%20as%20someone%20great%20by%20those%20in%20the%20world.%20Such%20pursuit%2C%20however%2C%20leads%20to%20three%20main%20areas%20of%20sin%3A%20intellectual%20pride%2C%20lustful%20passion%2C%20and%20greed.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJeremiah%20warned%20that%20a%20wise%20man%20shouldn't%20boast%20of%20his%20wisdom%20any%20more%20than%20a%20strong%20man%20should%20boast%20of%20his%20strength%20or%20a%20rich%20man%20of%20his%20wealth.%20Why%3F%20Because%20those%20wise%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20rich%20men%20produced%20none%20of%20those%20characteristics%20in%20their%20lives.%20It%20was%20God%20alone%20who%20gave%20them%20whatever%20wisdom%2C%20strength%2C%20or%20riches%20they%20possess.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPaul%20reminded%20the%20Colossians%2C%20%22For%20you%20died%20when%20Christ%20died%2C%20and%20your%20real%20life%20is%20hidden%20with%20Christ%20in%20God%22%20(Colossians%203%3A3).%20We%20must%20put%20to%20death%20the%20proud%20mind%20of%20man%20that%20flatters%20and%20exalts%20himself%20in%20his%20own%20eyes.%20We%20must%20crucify%20the%20sinful%20desires%20of%20the%20flesh%2C%20such%20as%20%22sexual%20sin%2C%20impurity%2C%20lust%2C%20and%20shameful%20desires%22%20(v.%205).%20Furthermore%2C%20we%20cannot%20%22be%20greedy%20for%20the%20good%20things%20of%20this%20life%2C%20for%20that%20is%20idolatry%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(v.%205).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20we%20boast%20of%20anything%20in%20this%20world%2C%20it%20should%20only%20be%20the%20awesome%20fact%20that%20we%20understand%20and%20know%20the%20Lord%20personally.%20In%20everything%20else%2C%20let%20us%20put%20on%20humility%2C%20purity%2C%20and%20generosity.%20The%20world%20may%20not%20appreciate%20us%20when%20we%20do%2C%20but%20in%20God's%20eyes%20we%20will%20be%20pursuing%20true%20wisdom%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20riches!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
