            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%208%3A8-9%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BHow%20can%20you%20say%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20are%20wise%20because%20we%20have%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhen%20your%20teachers%20have%20twisted%20it%20by%20writing%20lies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20wise%20teachers%20will%20fall%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Einto%20the%20trap%20of%20their%20own%20foolishness%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Efor%20they%20have%20rejected%20the%20word%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EAre%20they%20so%20wise%20after%20all%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20give%20their%20wives%20to%20others%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20their%20farms%20to%20strangers.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFrom%20the%20least%20to%20the%20greatest%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Etheir%20lives%20are%20ruled%20by%20greed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EYes%2C%20even%20my%20prophets%20and%20priests%20are%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20are%20all%20frauds.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20offer%20superficial%20treatments%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20my%20people%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mortal%20wound.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20give%20assurances%20of%20peace%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhen%20there%20is%20no%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAre%20they%20ashamed%20of%20these%20disgusting%20actions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ENot%20at%20all%26%23x2014%3Bthey%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20know%20how%20to%20blush!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETherefore%2C%20they%20will%20lie%20among%20the%20slaughtered.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20will%20be%20brought%20down%20when%20I%20punish%20them%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esays%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20surely%20consume%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20more%20harvests%20of%20figs%20and%20grapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ETheir%20fruit%20trees%20will%20all%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWhatever%20I%20gave%20them%20will%20soon%20be%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20the%20people%20will%20say%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BWhy%20should%20we%20wait%20here%20to%20die%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ECome%2C%20let%26%23x2019%3Bs%20go%20to%20the%20fortified%20towns%20and%20die%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20has%20decreed%20our%20destruction%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eand%20has%20given%20us%20a%20cup%20of%20poison%20to%20drink%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebecause%20we%20sinned%20against%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20hoped%20for%20peace%2C%20but%20no%20peace%20came.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWe%20hoped%20for%20a%20time%20of%20healing%2C%20but%20found%20only%20terror.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20snorting%20of%20the%20enemies%26%23x2019%3B%20warhorses%20can%20be%20heard%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eall%20the%20way%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Dan%20in%20the%20north!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20neighing%20of%20their%20stallions%20makes%20the%20whole%20land%20tremble.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThey%20are%20coming%20to%20devour%20the%20land%20and%20everything%20in%20it%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecities%20and%20people%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20send%20these%20enemy%20troops%20among%20you%3C%2Fp%3E%